            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Nehemiah.9:22-10:39",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ENehemiah%209%3A22-10%3A39%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_22%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20you%20helped%20our%20ancestors%20conquer%20kingdoms%20and%20nations%2C%20and%20you%20placed%20your%20people%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20land.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A22%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20They%20took%20over%20the%20land%20of%20King%20Sihon%20of%20Heshbon%20and%20the%20land%20of%20King%20Og%20of%20Bashan.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_23%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20made%20their%20descendants%20as%20numerous%20as%20the%20stars%20in%20the%20sky%20and%20brought%20them%20into%20the%20land%20you%20had%20promised%20to%20their%20ancestors.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_24%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThey%20went%20in%20and%20took%20possession%20of%20the%20land.%20You%20subdued%20whole%20nations%20before%20them.%20Even%20the%20Canaanites%2C%20who%20inhabited%20the%20land%2C%20were%20powerless!%20Your%20people%20could%20deal%20with%20these%20nations%20and%20their%20kings%20as%20they%20pleased.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_25%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EOur%20ancestors%20captured%20fortified%20cities%20and%20fertile%20land.%20They%20took%20over%20houses%20full%20of%20good%20things%2C%20with%20cisterns%20already%20dug%20and%20vineyards%20and%20olive%20groves%20and%20fruit%20trees%20in%20abundance.%20So%20they%20ate%20until%20they%20were%20full%20and%20grew%20fat%20and%20enjoyed%20themselves%20in%20all%20your%20blessings.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_26%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20despite%20all%20this%2C%20they%20were%20disobedient%20and%20rebelled%20against%20you.%20They%20turned%20their%20backs%20on%20your%20Law%2C%20they%20killed%20your%20prophets%20who%20warned%20them%20to%20return%20to%20you%2C%20and%20they%20committed%20terrible%20blasphemies.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_27%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20you%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20their%20enemies%2C%20who%20made%20them%20suffer.%20But%20in%20their%20time%20of%20trouble%20they%20cried%20to%20you%2C%20and%20you%20heard%20them%20from%20heaven.%20In%20your%20great%20mercy%2C%20you%20sent%20them%20liberators%20who%20rescued%20them%20from%20their%20enemies.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_28%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20were%20at%20peace%2C%20your%20people%20again%20committed%20evil%20in%20your%20sight%2C%20and%20once%20more%20you%20let%20their%20enemies%20conquer%20them.%20Yet%20whenever%20your%20people%20turned%20and%20cried%20to%20you%20again%20for%20help%2C%20you%20listened%20once%20more%20from%20heaven.%20In%20your%20wonderful%20mercy%2C%20you%20rescued%20them%20many%20times!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_29%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20warned%20them%20to%20return%20to%20your%20Law%2C%20but%20they%20became%20proud%20and%20obstinate%20and%20disobeyed%20your%20commands.%20They%20did%20not%20follow%20your%20regulations%2C%20by%20which%20people%20will%20find%20life%20if%20only%20they%20obey.%20They%20stubbornly%20turned%20their%20backs%20on%20you%20and%20refused%20to%20listen.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_30%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20your%20love%2C%20you%20were%20patient%20with%20them%20for%20many%20years.%20You%20sent%20your%20Spirit%2C%20who%20warned%20them%20through%20the%20prophets.%20But%20still%20they%20wouldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20listen!%20So%20once%20again%20you%20allowed%20the%20peoples%20of%20the%20land%20to%20conquer%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_31%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20in%20your%20great%20mercy%2C%20you%20did%20not%20destroy%20them%20completely%20or%20abandon%20them%20forever.%20What%20a%20gracious%20and%20merciful%20God%20you%20are!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_32%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20now%2C%20our%20God%2C%20the%20great%20and%20mighty%20and%20awesome%20God%2C%20who%20keeps%20his%20covenant%20of%20unfailing%20love%2C%20do%20not%20let%20all%20the%20hardships%20we%20have%20suffered%20seem%20insignificant%20to%20you.%20Great%20trouble%20has%20come%20upon%20us%20and%20upon%20our%20kings%20and%20leaders%20and%20priests%20and%20prophets%20and%20ancestors%26%23x2014%3Ball%20of%20your%20people%26%23x2014%3Bfrom%20the%20days%20when%20the%20kings%20of%20Assyria%20first%20triumphed%20over%20us%20until%20now.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_33%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EEvery%20time%20you%20punished%20us%20you%20were%20being%20just.%20We%20have%20sinned%20greatly%2C%20and%20you%20gave%20us%20only%20what%20we%20deserved.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_34%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EOur%20kings%2C%20leaders%2C%20priests%2C%20and%20ancestors%20did%20not%20obey%20your%20Law%20or%20listen%20to%20the%20warnings%20in%20your%20commands%20and%20laws.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_35%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EEven%20while%20they%20had%20their%20own%20kingdom%2C%20they%20did%20not%20serve%20you%2C%20though%20you%20showered%20your%20goodness%20on%20them.%20You%20gave%20them%20a%20large%2C%20fertile%20land%2C%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20turn%20from%20their%20wickedness.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_36%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20now%20today%20we%20are%20slaves%20in%20the%20land%20of%20plenty%20that%20you%20gave%20our%20ancestors%20for%20their%20enjoyment!%20We%20are%20slaves%20here%20in%20this%20good%20land.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_37%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20lush%20produce%20of%20this%20land%20piles%20up%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20kings%20whom%20you%20have%20set%20over%20us%20because%20of%20our%20sins.%20They%20have%20power%20over%20us%20and%20our%20livestock.%20We%20serve%20them%20at%20their%20pleasure%2C%20and%20we%20are%20in%20great%20misery.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_9_38%22